{"tid":648631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石棺案阿豪反駁阿T指控 稱小草有公主病","createTime":"2018-04-30T22:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T01:33:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9cd61e1b4fb944be6e96894cd8a7c2ec07e526","tid":648631,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T22:38:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=W5QmFJY5hwVuk6%2FN%2FfnFXC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fdb27966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】荃灣工廈石棺藏屍案今日(30日)續審，警方向次被告劉錫豪(花名「阿豪」)播放「小草」何菱瑜的錄影口供，「小草」在錄影口供提及的案發經過，大致上與她在庭上證供差不多，她指案發時她在閣樓睡覺，看不見行兇經過，她聽到「X你老母」及「唔唔聲」的反抗聲音後，首被告曾祥欣(花名「阿T」)被叫到樓下幫手，當時她繼續睡覺，及後從曾的口中得知死者已死。<br />\n<br />\n之後曾及劉外出買繩及麻包袋等物資，「小草」問第三被告張善恒：「點解會喺屋企死咗？唔係話唔會死㗎咩？」她指事前曾向她提及，他們原意只想在單位迷暈死者，再替死者打酒精針，佯裝死者飲醉，然後才將死者運到單位以外其他地方殺死。她聽到死者已死之後，不知如何反應，還以為曾在講笑。<br />\n<br />\n「小草」指，曾祥欣威脅她知情不報也要坐監10年8年，曾又向她稱可將所有罪名推到她身上，她「驚得滯」，因此跟隨3名被告潛逃到台灣。她又透露自己任職侍應，與3名被告均是朋友關係，搬到DAN6單位之前與母親及妹妹同住在元朗楊屋新村。<br />\n<br />\n劉錫豪看畢曾祥欣及「小草」與警方錄取的口供後，他再與警方進行另一次錄影會面，他向警方逐一反駁曾祥欣的版本。他指打劫死者是曾祥欣及張善恒的主意，曾、張二人事前圖用谷歌地圖搜尋行兇地點，案發時他正在睡覺，但二人卻「夾口供」，將他說成是行兇者。此外，他親眼目睹曾在死者的腳背刺刀放血，但曾卻沒有向警方提及有肢解死者及放血的事。他認為曾對他的指控根本是「九唔搭八」，「完全將事實掉番轉嚟講」。<br />\n<br />\n劉向警員表示，他及張善恒都曾經被曾祥欣騙財，他說：「黐線㗎，一個27歲呃過咁多人嘅人(曾祥欣)，乜都賴晒我，搵鬼信咩？」他反對「小草」跟隨他們潛逃到台灣，因認為「小草」是一位有「公主病」的女生，帶同她一起潛逃只會令他們在台灣的生活更麻煩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hVQhF4kRf.VFZLtGWdLgpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/2003765c1519e0bacb30bc81a401d9b8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhVQhF4kRf.VFZLtGWdLgpg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F2003765c1519e0bacb30bc81a401d9b8&h=f6b89738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kab3nZduj6BcIUn0_o_Znw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/1f55bfa86ff0eb77086847c81918aae8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fkab3nZduj6BcIUn0_o_Znw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F1f55bfa86ff0eb77086847c81918aae8&h=ab9090b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9F%B3%E6%A3%BA%E6%A1%88%E9%98%BF%E8%B1%AA%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E9%98%BFt%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%8F%E8%8D%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E7%97%85-094123233.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25A3%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2598%25BF%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25A7%2581%25E9%2598%25BFt%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%2597%2585-094123233.html&d=W5QmFJY5hwVuk6%2FN%2FfnFXC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a2354149\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9F%B3%E6%A3%BA%E6%A1%88%E9%98%BF%E8%B1%AA%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E9%98%BFt%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%8F%E8%8D%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E7%97%85-094123233.html</a>"},{"pid":"916b27c06b6c0a148df02e1be80f8b306aed0de9","tid":648631,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"小草有訓覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa16f7f2d0489cf1907d05b5e387bce7dc01f5c5","tid":648631,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨 個個都推莊唔認殺人想坐小啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}